attributeSource.infoString2: Coldwell Banker Residential Brokerage - Evanston-Central

data.description: Welcome to your dream home in desirable Evanston! This stunning brick 2-flat offers the perfect blend of classic charm and modern convenience. Step inside to find spacious units flooded with natural light, boasting new flooring, brand new appliances, and fresh paint throughout. With 2 bedrooms on the first floor and 3 bedrooms on the second, there's plenty of space for everyone. Both units feature cozy den areas, perfect for relaxing or entertaining.  The basement provides huge designated storage areas, along with laundry facilities and mechanicals, ensuring convenience at every turn. Recent updates include a new hot water tank, boiler, tuck-pointing, back porch, and roof, giving you peace of mind for years to come. Outside, the property shines with new porch, a fully fenced backyard, and a backdrop of scenic Hinman Park.  Conveniently located within walking distance to the EL, Metra, and Lake (south blvd beach), this home offers easy access to everything Evanston has to offer. Don't miss your chance to make this your forever home! Schedule a showing today and experience the charm of Evanston living at its finest. Great Investment opportunity! Excellent NOI!
